<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.4.10">
<l>varuntirai maṇinīrk kaṅkaiyiṉ karaimēl</l>
<l>vatariyāc ciramat tuḷḷāṉai</l>
<l>karuṅkaṭal munnīr vaṇṇaṉai yeṇṇik</l>
<l>kaliyaṉvā yoliceyta paṉuval</l>
<l>varañceyta vaintu maintumval lārkaḷ</l>
<l>vāṉava rulakuṭaṉ maruvi</l>
<l>iruṅkaṭa lulaka māṇṭuveṇ kuṭaikkī</l>
<l>ḻimaiyava rākuvar tāmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these five-plus-five [verses] composed with merit,</l>
<l rend="indent">the text composed of poems by Kaliyaṉ,</l>
<l>Contemplating the one whose hue is of the dark sea’s three-waters,</l>
<l rend="indent">the one who is in Badarī Āśrama</l>
<l>On the banks of the Ganges where crystal waters arrive in waves,</l>
<l rend="indent">they will become unblinking [celestials]</l>
<l>Under a white umbrella, ruling the world with the vast sea,</l>
<l rend="indent">joining with the world of heavenly beings.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
